{
  "title": "Fermented Dense Mediterranean Kabanos Tagine",
  "description": "A hearty, high-protein feast featuring fermented kabanos sausages, chickpeas, and aromatic spices. This slow-cooked tagine is perfect for a festive dinner gathering.",
